 <text>
  <front>
   <head>TO MR *****</head>
  </front>
  <body>
   <lg xmlns="http://www.tei-c.org/ns/1.0" type="poem">
    <lg n="1" stanza_type="quatrain">
     <l n="1" met="-+|-+|-+|-+" line_length="8">Unus'd to every soothing sound,</l>
     <l n="2" met="-+|-+|-+" line_length="6">Inur'd to every sorrow;</l>
     <l n="3" met="-+|-+|-+|-+" line_length="8">To day you vainly bind the wound</l>
     <l n="4" met="-+|-+|-+" line_length="6">That bleeds afresh to-morrow.</l>
    </lg>
    <lg n="2" stanza_type="quatrain">
     <l n="5" met="-+|-+|-+|-+" line_length="8">The world beholds with careless eye,</l>
     <l n="6" met="-+|-+|-+" line_length="6">And much I scorn their pity;</l>
     <l n="7" met="-+|-+|-+|-+" line_length="8">Unseen, to heave the bursting sigh,</l>
     <l n="8" met="-+|-+|-+" line_length="6">I leave the crowded city.</l>
    </lg>
    <lg n="3" stanza_type="quatrain">
     <l n="9" met="-+|-+|-+|-+" line_length="8">And dost thou ask my falt'ring tongue,</l>
     <l n="10" met="-+|-+|-+" line_length="6">To tell a tale of woe?</l>
     <l n="11" met="-+|-+|-+|-+" line_length="8">The griefs my youthful breast have wrung</l>
     <l n="12" met="-+|-+|-+" line_length="6">Oh! may'st thou never know!</l>
    </lg>
    <lg n="4" stanza_type="quatrain">
     <l n="13" met="-+|-+|-+|-+" line_length="8">Long have I bore an orphan's name,</l>
     <l n="14" met="-+|-+|-+" line_length="6">And shar'd an orphan's fate;</l>
     <l n="15" met="-+|-+|-+|-+" line_length="8">Few friends I have, or dare to claim,</l>
     <l n="16" met="-+|-+|-+" line_length="6">Such is my helpless state.</l>
    </lg>
    <lg n="5" stanza_type="quatrain">
     <l n="17" met="-+|-+|-+|-+" line_length="8">The simple dictates of my heart</l>
     <l n="18" met="-+|-+|-+" line_length="6">To public view they force;</l>
     <l n="19" met="-+|-+|-+|-+" line_length="8">Not pride, but pain does this impart;</l>
     <l n="20" met="-+|-+|-+" line_length="6">It is my last resource.</l>
    </lg>
   </lg>
